'''David Pittu''' is an [[Wikipedia:Actor|actor]] and [[Wikipedia:Voice acting|audiobook narrator]]. Pittu is known for narrating a number of children's books such as [[Wikipedia:A-Z mysteries|A-Z mysteries]] and [[Wikipedia:39 Clues|39 Clues]].<ref name="Audiofile interview" /> For ''[[Star Wars]]'' Pittu narrated the [[The Han Solo Omnibus|audiobooks]] for ''[[The Han Solo Trilogy]]'' by [[A. C. Crispin]].<ref name="Han Solo Omnibus">[[The Han Solo Omnibus|''The Han Solo Omnibus'' audiobook collection]]</ref>

